        <title>New malloc trace implementation</title>
        <body>This change implements a malloc trace without using the now deprecated glibc malloc hooks. This means the feature is now available on musl-based system and MacOsX too. In addition it can also track memory reclamation, so it can track the currently alive memory.

fixes #1550

</body>
